    Class Description
    Controller
    The controller for the word trainer (a word guessing game)
    GameControl
    A component that displays the user some statistics for the word trainer and provides buttons to control the game
    ImageDisplay
    A component that displays an image from the internet to the user
    ImageLoadingError  
    Layout
    Initializes and positions all parts of the UI in a border layout
    Main
    Run the WordTrainer
    ModelTest
    Tests for the pdamianik.model
    Quiz
    A component to ask the user for a word
    SerializedFileIO
    Contains methods to save and load a WordTrainer via the java internal object serialization
    TextFileIO
    Contains methods to save and load a WordTrainer via a custom serialization method
    Window
    A universal JFrame to house any JPanel
    WordEntry
    A word and a picture (in form of an URL to the image) that shows the meaning of the word
    WordList
    Stores a list of WordEntry
    WordTrainer
    A word trainer that stores combinations of a word in form of a string and a image displaying the meaning of the word as an URL and compares a provided word with the selected word
